{"tid":930741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"KFC: 3指手套能夠方便食客用手機","createTime":"2018-12-06T13:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T06:47:00.000Z","uid":42188,"like":12,"dislike":173,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"93be3a08cf546aab8c016284775512d3ab7cc540","tid":930741,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:54:16.000Z","msg":"其實這是 KFC 肯德基家鄉雞自家開發設計的「三指手套」，是故意只遮住 3 隻手指，更是順應了兩個大潮流，包括：環保，與及玩手機！<br />\n<br />\nKFC 肯德基家鄉雞自家設計的這款「三指手套」，<span style=\"color: red;\">除了環保，還可方便食客，邊食肯德基家鄉雞，邊玩手機！</span>這款「三指手套」由日本 KFC 花了長時間研發，已於今年 7 月 27 日搶先在日本推出，稱為「ゆびキレイ」（手指漂亮），只會套着姆指、食指、中指及一半掌心。除了環保，還盼望可令女生用手食雞食得更優雅，可以用未被包住的無名指和尾指玩手機，方便機不離手的低頭族。注意 KFC 肯德基家鄉雞餐廳的「三指手套」不會主動向食客提供。"},{"pid":"6c62e4189d3fe99059bb04a66d23e1b10949bbc1","tid":930741,"uid":153239,"like":52,"dislike":3,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"環保撚要邀功架 <br />\n你黎阻頭阻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係佢地迫到KFC換手套！"},{"pid":"ef220a0368034fb7987f0853170f066ca80fb3b7","tid":930741,"uid":202051,"like":276,"dislike":3,"score":273,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...點解唔好似正常人咁一隻手食野一隻手用手機?"},{"pid":"27e8540577bb92db3b711a929649d3ad8047858c","tid":930741,"uid":59011,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁個手機殻會油過家鄉雞"},{"pid":"0f2501c5a95542240c8ec0154a6029d9dd76045d","tid":930741,"uid":13638,"like":124,"dislike":0,"score":124,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"用另一隻手咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb0b7bc3a2523936730c9ec720963873e0672d0","tid":930741,"uid":1654,"like":85,"dislike":2,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T14:02:09.000Z","msg":"邊個會用個兩隻手指玩手機"},{"pid":"7f4b2aa446b115ea015d87eb419c8a0b